.Dd December 3, 1999
.Dt DOPOWERHOOKS 9
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm dopowerhooks
.Nd run all power hooks
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Ft void
.Fn doshutdownhooks "int why"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn dopowerhooks
function invokes all power hooks established using the
.Xr powerhook_establish 9
function.  Power hooks are called in reverse order, i.e.,
the power hook established last will be called first.
.Pp
This function is called from the
.Xr apm 4
driver when a power change is detected.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr powerhook_establish 9
